data.description: Welcome home to your charm in the city.  This ALL BRICK, 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, PLUS FLEX SPACE home is waiting for you!  Entering through the cheery yellow front door, you will find an updated living room, dining area and kitchen with modern all white cabinets.  A large interior mudroom/laundry room is the perfect spot for storage.  The HUGE flex space is waiting for you to make it your own, office, playroom, media room, game room, your choice! Step into the large backyard  and you will find an oversized two car carport plus plenty of room for a fire pit, pets, kids, and grilling out. This is the home you have been looking for!! Convenient to top rated schools, Kingsbay Naval Base, I-95, beaches, Jacksonville International Airport and more!
